<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-1a' );" name="006-1a" class="pb">[006-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　三家詩拾遺卷六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:221'>　　　　　　　　　　栁州府知府范家相撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='221:226'>　國風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='226:230'>葛屦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='230:250'>摻摻女手<span class='krp-note'>摻韓/作<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1021' title='KR1021' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1021.png'/></span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='250:291'>　韓詩内傳<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1021' title='KR1021' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1021.png'/><img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1021' title='KR1021' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1021.png'/>女手之貌<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span>　古詩纎纎出素手</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='291:297'>　　本此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='297:323'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-1b' );" name="006-1b" class="pb">[006-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='323:328'>汾沮洳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='328:349'>　齊詩匡衡曰晉侯好儉而民畜聚<span class='krp-note'>奏/疏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='349:372'>　　儉為美徳能畜聚則户有葢藏家給人足矣如匡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='372:381'>　　衡則非刺也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='381:386'>園有桃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='386:392'>我歌且謡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='392:412'>　韓詩有章曲曰歌無章曲曰謠<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='412:416'>伐檀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='416:442'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-2a' );" name="006-2a" class="pb">[006-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='442:466'>　齊詩張楫曰伐檀刺賢者不遇明王也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='466:489'>　　張氏之説與毛畧同按孔叢子曰伐檀見賢者之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='489:512'>　　先事後食也與孟子答公孫丑之意正同董仲舒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='512:535'>　　及薛漢之説皆然毛傳謂在位貪鄙賢者不得仕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='535:553'>　　進張楫謂賢者不遇明王俱非詩意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='553:568'>彼君子兮不素餐兮　不素食兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='568:591'>　韓詩薛君章句曰何為素餐素餐者質也人但有質</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='591:614'>　樸而無治民之才名曰素餐尸禄者頗有所知善惡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='614:640'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-2b' );" name="006-2b" class="pb">[006-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='640:665'>　不明黙然不語苟欲得禄而已譬如尸焉<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='665:688'>　　狩獵稼穡有位之君子如此可謂質矣而又能蒞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='688:711'>　　官治民是謂不素餐之君子能不素餐則亦不尸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='711:717'>　　禄矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='717:739'>　董仲舒曰不素食兮先其事後其食謂之治身也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='739:747'>河水清且淪漪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='747:765'>　韓詩順流而風曰淪文貌<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='765:769'>蟋蟀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='769:795'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-3a' );" name="006-3a" class="pb">[006-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='795:801'>嵗聿其莫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='801:824'>　韓詩薛君章句曰聿辭也莫晚也言君子之年嵗已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='824:835'>　晚也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='835:858'>　　不曰嵗晚而曰君子之年歳已晚猶云老冉冉其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='858:881'>　　将至勸其及時為樂也君子良士之稱此非刺晉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='881:904'>　　僖儉不中禮之意甚明季札聞歌唐而嘆其憂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='904:927'>　　深有陶唐之遺民孔叢子曰於唐見儉德之大也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='927:947'>　　思深而有儉德無已太康職思其居之謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='947:973'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-3b' );" name="006-3b" class="pb">[006-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='973:978'>山有樞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='978:1001'>　魯詩司馬遷曰當周公召公共和之時成侯曾孫僖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1001:1028'>　侯甚嗇愛物儉不中禮國人閔之唐之變風始作<span class='krp-note'>史/記</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1028:1039'>子有酒食何不日鼓瑟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1039:1062'>　魯詩傳曰天子食日舉樂諸侯不釋縣大夫士日琴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1062:1076'>　瑟<span class='krp-note'>公羊傳注/引魯傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1076:1099'>　　此本曲禮文而魯詩引之以明上下皆不可斯須</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1099:1113'>　　去樂之意非専指下位也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1113:1139'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-4a' );" name="006-4a" class="pb">[006-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1139:1144'>揚之水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1144:1176'>素衣朱襮<span class='krp-note'>襮魯/作綃</span>　魯詩内傳綃綺屬<span class='krp-note'>鄭注士昏/禮引魯傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1176:1180'>綢繆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1180:1193'>見此邂逅<span class='krp-note'>逅韓/作覯</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1193:1211'>　韓詩内傳邂逅不固之貌<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1211:1234'>　　卒然幸遇不可乆長故曰不固毛傳别本亦作邂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1234:1248'>　　逅釋文解説也與韓異義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1248:1254'>有杕之杜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1254:1280'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-4b' );" name="006-4b" class="pb">[006-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1280:1293'>噬肯適我<span class='krp-note'>噬韓/作逝</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1293:1320'>　韓詩内傳逝及也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>　言猶及君子之在而幸其適</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1320:1343'>　　我而飲食欵留之也分明幸見君子而愛之之詞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1343:1347'>車粼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1347:1373'>寺人之令<span class='krp-note'>韓作/伶</span>　韓詩傳曰伶使伶也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1373:1377'>小戎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1377:1383'>俴駟孔羣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1383:1401'>　韓詩駟馬不着甲曰俴駟<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1401:1427'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-5a' );" name="006-5a" class="pb">[006-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1427:1450'>　　按鄭箋以俴駟為四介馬孔疏以淺薄之金為甲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1450:1473'>　　而韓以為不着甲何也鞌之戰不介而馳春秋時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1473:1488'>　　固已有之秦人剽疾或類與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1488:1492'>蒹葭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1492:1510'>　韓詩薛君曰大渚如沚<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1510:1514'>終南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1514:1546'>顔如渥丹<span class='krp-note'>丹韓/作沰</span>　韓詩傳曰沰<span class='krp-note'>撻各/切</span>赭也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1546:1550'>黄鳥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1550:1576'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-5b' );" name="006-5b" class="pb">[006-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1576:1598'>　齊詩匡衡曰秦伯貴信而民多從死<span class='krp-note'>奏/疏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1598:1621'>　　應劭曰秦穆公與羣臣飲酣言曰生共此樂死共</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1621:1645'>　　此哀于是奄息仲行緘虎許諾及公薨皆從死故李</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1645:1669'>　　德裕論曰若三良者殉榮樂非殉仁義也此貴信之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1669:1693'>　　説也史記穆公𦵏于雍從死者百七十人此民多</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1693:1704'>　　從死非獨三良也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1704:1708'>晨風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1708:1732'>□彼晨風　韓詩□作鷸謂鷸乗朝風而飛也其義不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1732:1758'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-6a' );" name="006-6a" class="pb">[006-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1758:1781'>　　六書故亦以晨風為朝風漢魏人則以晨風為鸇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1781:1785'>渭陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1785:1808'>　魯詩劉向曰重耳入秦秦送之晉太子罃思母之恩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1808:1830'>　而送舅氏曰我送舅氏曰至渭陽<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1830:1834'>宛丘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1834:1861'>　齊詩匡衡曰陳夫人好巫而民多淫祀<span class='krp-note'>奏/疏</span>　班固曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1861:1884'>　周武王封媯滿于陳是為胡公妻以元女大姬婦人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='1884:1907'>　尊貴好祭祀用巫故其俗好巫鬼者也詩稱擊鼓于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='1907:1933'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-6b' );" name="006-6b" class="pb">[006-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='1933:1957'>　宛丘之上婆娑于枌𣗳之下是有大姬歌舞之遺風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='1957:1967'>　也<span class='krp-note'>地理/志</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='1967:1990'>　　按季札聞歌陳而嘆曰國無主其能乆乎國之無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='1990:2013'>　　主者民皆淫祀忘其本業而上不禁止之謂非必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2013:2036'>　　以宛丘之子即為陳主也班氏故以是詩與東門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2036:2059'>　　之枌並舉夫民化其上而上與下如出一心非刺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2059:2067'>　　其君而何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2067:2090'>東門之枌　榖旦于差韓詩作嗟謂擇令日而招同類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2090:2116'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-7a' );" name="006-7a" class="pb">[006-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2116:2130'>　猶嗟我婦子之嗟亦偹一説</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2130:2149'>衡門　可以樂饑韓詩作可以療饑義亦異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2149:2171'>東門之池　魯詩孔安國曰停水曰池<span class='krp-note'>鄭/箋</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2171:2175'>墓門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2175:2198'>　魯詩劉向曰陳辨女陳之采桑女也魯大夫解居使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2198:2221'>　于陳遇采桑之女止而戲之曰子為我歌吾将舍女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2221:2244'>　乃歌曰墓門有棘斧以斯之夫也不良國人知之又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2244:2267'>　曰為我歌其二女曰墓門有梅有鴞萃止夫也不良</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2267:2293'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-7b' );" name="006-7b" class="pb">[006-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2293:2316'>　歌以訊之大夫曰其棘則是其鴞安在女曰陳小國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2316:2339'>　也攝乎大國之間加之以師旅因之以饑饉其人且</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2339:2358'>　亡而況鴞乎乃服而舍之<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2358:2381'>　　此謂辨女歌墓門之詩非謂作墓門之詩也其曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2381:2404'>　　人且亡而況鴞乎借詩比刺于本義不涉楚辭何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2404:2434'>　　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2848' title='KR2848' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2848.png'/>鳥萃棘而縱子肆情王逸注曰解居父聘呉過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2434:2457'>　　陳之墓門見婦負其子欲與之淫佚婦人引詩刺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2457:2480'>　　之其説尤明諸家好竒竟有以墓門一詩為辨女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2480:2506'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-8a' );" name="006-8a" class="pb">[006-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2506:2529'>　　作者未之考也但墓門是地非丘墓之門與左傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2529:2541'>　　正同故節而辨之焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2541:2558'>歌以訊之　韓詩訊諫也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2558:2586'>防有鵲巢　誰侜予美<span class='krp-note'>韓作/娓</span>韓内傳娓美也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2586:2609'>澤陂　傷如之何<span class='krp-note'>石經/作陽</span>魯詩傳曰陽予也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2609:2639'>碩大且卷<span class='krp-note'>韓卷/作㜝</span>　韓詩薛君曰㜝重頥也<span class='krp-note'>太平/御覽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2639:2643'>匪風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2643:2684'>匪風發兮匪車偈兮<span class='krp-note'>偈韓/作掲</span>顧瞻周道中心怛兮<span class='krp-note'>怛韓作/<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1826' title='KR1826' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1826.png'/>古怛</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2684:2710'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-8b' );" name="006-8b" class="pb">[006-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2710:2716'><span class='krp-note'>字/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2716:2739'>　韓詩外傳成周之時隂陽調寒暑平羣生遂萬物寧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2739:2762'>　故曰其風治其樂逹其驅馬也舒其民依依其行遲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2762:2785'>　遲其意好好詩曰匪風發兮匪車掲兮顧瞻周道中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2785:2815'>　心<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1826' title='KR1826' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1826.png'/>兮王吉曰是非古之風也發發者是非古之車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2815:2832'>　也掲掲者葢傷之也<span class='krp-note'>疏引/詩</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2832:2855'>　　舉古之風與車以慨今之不然即周道之所見以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2855:2877'>　　興成周之道也故卒章曰誰将西歸懷之好音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2877:2903'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-9a' );" name="006-9a" class="pb">[006-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2903:2907'>候人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2907:2935'>荷戈與祋<span class='krp-note'>祋韓/作綴</span>　維鵜在梁不濡其翼彼其之子不稱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='2935:2939'>其服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='2939:2962'>　韓詩鄭康成曰汚澤善居泥水之中在魚梁以不濡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='2962:2986'>　其翼為才如君子以不稱其服為有德<span class='krp-note'>表記/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='2986:3009'>　　王應麟曰此韓詩説也　言汚澤之鳥尚以不濡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3009:3032'>　　其翼為才況為君子而在上可以不稱其服乎國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3032:3055'>　　語載楚子引詩曰彼其之子不遂其媾郵之也郵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3055:3081'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-9b' );" name="006-9b" class="pb">[006-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3081:3093'>　　與尤通葢古説已深</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3093:3097'>鳲鳩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3097:3120'>鳲鳩在桑其子七兮淑人君子其儀一兮其儀一兮心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3120:3125'>如結兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3125:3148'>　魯詩傳曰鳲鳩之所以飬七子者一心也君子所以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3148:3168'>　理萬物者一儀也<span class='krp-note'>説苑引魯/詩傳文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3168:3191'>　　按荀子曰其儀一兮心如結兮故君子結于一也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3191:3214'>　　此魯説之本唯心結于一而不二斯儀見於外而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3214:3241'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-10a' );" name="006-10a" class="pb">[006-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3241:3264'>　　如一儀一即不忒記曰其在朝廷則道仁聖禮義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3264:3287'>　　之序燕處則聽雅頌之音行步則有環珮之聲升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3287:3310'>　　車則有鸞和之音居處有禮進退有度百官得其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3310:3333'>　　宜萬事得其序故曰其儀不忒正是四國儀一之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3333:3356'>　　義大矣哉經傳皆美君子之詞毛以為刺者美古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3356:3376'>　　之君子以刺今之君之不一也其説一貫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3376:3380'>七月</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3380:3403'>　　歐陽修曰七月詩燕齊魯皆無之按太平御覽明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3403:3430'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-10b' );" name="006-10b" class="pb">[006-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3430:3453'>　　載韓嬰七月之説即釋文亦載有八月在宇之訓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3453:3476'>　　是韓詩之有七月甚明齊魯在宋時亡之已乆不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3476:3487'>　　知歐公此言何本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3487:3494'>四之日舉趾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3494:3520'>　韓詩傳曰言至于四月始可舉趾以耕也<span class='krp-note'>太平/御覽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3520:3531'>四月秀葽　獻豜于公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3531:3554'>　魯詩劉向曰秀葽味苦苦葽也　鄭氏曰四歳曰肩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3554:3563'>　<span class='krp-note'>周禮/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3563:3590'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-11a' );" name="006-11a" class="pb">[006-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3590:3613'>八月在宇　塞向墐户　嗟我婦子曰為改歳入此室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3613:3616'>處</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3616:3643'>　韓詩宇屋霤向北向忩也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>　班固曰曰為改歳入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3643:3667'>　此室處所以順隂陽備盜賊習禮文也<span class='krp-note'>白虎/通</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3667:3676'>二之日鑿氷冲冲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3676:3705'>　韓詩氷者窮谷隂氣所結不洩則化為伏隂<span class='krp-note'>初學記/引内傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3705:3728'>　　左傳言藏氷必取之深山窮谷固隂沍寒鑿而取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3728:3751'>　　之即以洩隂也可見王政之施無非節宣隂陽之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3751:3778'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-11b' );" name="006-11b" class="pb">[006-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3778:3783'>　　道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3783:3787'>鴟鴞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3787:3808'>　三家詩趙岐曰鴟鴞刺邠君也<span class='krp-note'>孟子/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3808:3831'>鴟鴞鴟鴞旣取我子無毁我室恩斯勤斯鬻子之閔斯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3831:3854'>　韓詩薛君曰䲭鴞鸋鴂鳥名也䲭鴞所以愛養其子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='3854:3877'>　者適以病之也愛養其子者謂堅固其窠巢病之者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='3877:3901'>　謂不知托于大𣗳茂枝反敷之葦䓟風至䓟折巢覆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='3901:3920'>　子死有卵則破是其病也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='3920:3947'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-12a' );" name="006-12a" class="pb">[006-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='3947:3970'>　　以鴟鴞為鸋鴂毛傳亦同但毛以䲭鴞托言人有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='3970:3993'>　　取其子者鴞若曰寧取我子無毁我巢以我積日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='3993:4016'>　　攻堅之故也薛則以䲭鴞指武庚謂其彌縫二叔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4016:4039'>　　不知自托于皇朝據國以叛終取滅亡就兩家之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4039:4062'>　　説觀之薛稍為近之小毖之詩曰肇允彼桃蟲桃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4062:4085'>　　蟲鷦鷯小鳥正鸋鴂之屬也䲭鴞的是鵂鶹墓門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4085:4115'>　　之詩曰有鴞萃止楚詞以為<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2848' title='KR2848' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2848.png'/>鳥豈鸋鴂乎金縢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4115:4138'>　　曰周公居東二年則罪人斯得乃為詩以貽王名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4138:4165'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-12b' );" name="006-12b" class="pb">[006-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4165:4188'>　　之曰鴟鴞罪人指武庚故以䲭鴞目之夫能毁人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4188:4209'>　　之室取人之子非鵂鶹而何集傳之説當矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4209:4232'>徹彼桑土<span class='krp-note'>土韓/作杜</span>　予手拮据　予所蓄租</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4232:4258'>　韓詩杜桑根也　口足為事曰拮据租積也<span class='krp-note'>俱釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4258:4286'>　　按方言云東齊謂根曰杜字林作<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2690' title='KR2690' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2690.png'/>桑皮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4286:4290'>東山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4290:4308'>鸛鳴于垤　烝在栗薪<span class='krp-note'>栗韓/作□</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4308:4331'>　韓詩薛君曰鸛水鳥巢居知風穴居知雨天将雨而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4331:4358'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-13a' );" name="006-13a" class="pb">[006-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4358:4389'>　蟻出壅土鸛見之長鳴而喜也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span>蓼薪衆薪也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4389:4406'>　　按鄭箋烝塵也栗析也義各不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4406:4417'>親結其䄜　九十其儀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4417:4444'>　韓詩薛君曰䄜帶也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span>外傳曰九十其儀言多儀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4444:4448'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4448:4452'>破斧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4452:4465'>四國是皇<span class='krp-note'>韓皇/作匡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4465:4488'>　白虎通周公東征四國是匡言周公東征述職而天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4488:4515'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-13b' );" name="006-13b" class="pb">[006-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4515:4538'>　下皆正也　按班氏之意謂東征歸國黜陟四國之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4538:4552'>　　臣而天下皆正此義亦新</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4552:4563'>又缺我錡　又缺我銶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4563:4579'>　韓詩錡木屬銶鑿屬<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4579:4583'>伐柯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4583:4593'>伐柯伐柯其則不逺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4593:4616'>　韓詩外傳原天命治人心理好惡適性情而治道偹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4616:4639'>　矣四者不求于外不假于人反諸已而已詩曰伐柯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4639:4666'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-14a' );" name="006-14a" class="pb">[006-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4666:4675'>　伐柯其則不逺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4675:4698'>　　外傳引詩即中庸以人治人之意非斷章取義古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4698:4721'>　　引此二句皆如是解毛傳曰以其所願乎上交乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4721:4744'>　　下以其所願乎下事乎上不逺求也引大學正與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4744:4763'>　　韓同葢美周公之善因人情以治人也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4763:4767'>九罭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4767:4785'>　韓詩九罭取鰕芘也<span class='krp-note'>太平/御覽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4785:4808'>　　毛以九罭為緵罟小魚之網鰕芘則益小矣孫炎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4808:4835'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '006-14b' );" name="006-14b" class="pb">[006-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4835:4853'>　　以為九囊之網則是大網朱子從之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4853:4856'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='4856:4859'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='4859:4862'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='4862:4865'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='4865:4868'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='4868:4871'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='4871:4881'>　三家詩拾遺卷六</span><br/>
</p>
